# Clean Architecture

## Layers (inward dependencies only)

```
domain/ → application/ → infra/ + interfaces/
```

- `src/domain/` — models, Zod schemas, errors; **no infra imports**
- `src/application/` — services, use cases, ports, QA tools
- `src/infra/` — Playwright, LLM, observation, persistence, config
- `src/interfaces/` — CLI controller

Module chain: `AppModule` → `InterfacesModule` → `ApplicationModule` → `InfraModule`.

## DI registration

- New service → `APPLICATION_PROVIDERS` in @src/application/application.module.ts
- New infra adapter → `INFRA_PROVIDERS` in @src/infra/infra.module.ts
- Inject ports via `@Inject('PortTokenName')`

## LangChain boundary

LangChain lives **only** in `src/infra/llm/`. It must not call Playwright, persist runtime state, or bypass Zod.

## ESM imports

Use `.js` suffix on relative imports (NodeNext):

```typescript
import { RunConfigSchema } from '../../domain/schemas/config.schema.js';
```

## Naming

kebab-case files; suffixes: `.service.ts`, `.usecase.ts`, `.provider.ts`, `.port.ts`, `.schema.ts`. Ports end with `Port`; no `any`.
